data.description: This contemporary, single-story residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, designed with an open floor plan that has tile throughout kitchen, dining, living and bathroom areas.  Revel in the luxury of energy-efficient Whirlpool appliances, expansive granite countertops, and stylish brushed nickel hardware included are smart home features such as the ability to open the garage door, access your AC from anywhere adding a touch of convenience. Additional highlights include a huge fenced in backyard that has public access to a canal that could be your new spot for a morning read with coffee. This 3-year-old gem is situated in a welcoming family-friendly community, offering not just a home but a lifestyle. Enjoy proximity to schools, stores, healthcare offices, 2 hospitals and the allure of the country's finest beaches in this thriving Palm Coast location. Don't miss this opportunity at this price!
